Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:53.31,FuckALIProject-eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,150)}Scowl at the world around you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.86,FuckALIProject-eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,150)}Let us destroy each other
