Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.41,FuckALIProject-eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,150)}Otherwise, with our wings and feet ripped from us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.04,FuckALIProject-eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,150)}we will rot away under this empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.25,FuckALIProject-eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,150)}There is a second me
