Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what \Na doppelganger is? {iirc, doppelganger without the umlaut is common in america}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A doppel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A second you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking abou—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were on your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I talked to him for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sty or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyelid is inflamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
