Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an8\b0\fscx100.000000\fs40.000000\fsp1.250000\c&HF2F2F2&\blur0.6\pos(1085.000000,568.750000)}- Karma -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be ninth graders next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fifteen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not looking forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have high \Nschool entry exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think? I kinda like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going \Nto buy it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to use you as a \Nmodel than using a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't really suit you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Too out of style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that eye \Nlets you see things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anything \Nwhen you look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how it's different \Nfrom your right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it called? \NHeterochromia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mismatched colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is too cute \Nfor an eye patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that some roundabout \Nway of calling yourself cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't deny it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I'll take that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang. It was cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have strange taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that elephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to a \Nreal amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How's next week sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom's going to be at a \Ndoll expo in Tokyo next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to watch the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If your mom{lit: my aunt [separated at birth etc]} isn't there, \NI can come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right outside. {lib: Yeah, I can see you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's April, so how come\Nthere is still snow here?{Also, why is there still snow \Nhere when it's already April?}{It's April, so why is it \Nstill snowing here? }{OR: It's April, so why is there still snow here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I love how you have so many beautiful dolls in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Siblings are second-degree relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Degree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents are first, grandparents and siblings are second, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some rumors \Ngoing around in my new class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your new class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any cool people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... kind of a weird class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's cursed, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what everyone is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That really is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So there aren't any \Ncool people in your class...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I introduce \Nyou to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You said there aren't any \Ncool guys in your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like an old woman \Nselling souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my aunt make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to \Nforgive our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean my aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She still thinks of \Nyou as her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But she feels bad \Nbecause of the adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't forgiven \Nherself for giving you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure she's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, c'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't resent her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Kirika \Nfeels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She separated two sisters.{She stole one child of a pair.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But even more so, she's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's worried that I might \Ngo back to my real mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why we're not \Nallowed to hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't blame her. {I can't say I don't understand it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good idea for \Nnewcomers to stay down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The dolls are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My room has four and a \Nhalf tatami mats and a futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a room like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start acting so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're twins; we're the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Except I was born a few \Nminutes before you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think whoever's \Nstronger is the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Working girls are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it \Nlooks to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lot more \Nthin than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm thin, \Nyou might not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, haven't you grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's fr-freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you become \Nsuch a pervert, Misaki? {lit: perverted old man / lecher / etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you \Nthink we've bathed together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember our childhood, but maybe two or three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when our first was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe fifth grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When granny Amane let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I guessed it earlier. We just look too much alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any baby pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured they wouldn't throw 'em out, so I searched the house for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I did find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The pictures from \Nwhen we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I were lying \Nside by side on those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the same exact face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the \Namusement park tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember? \NThe one Mom took us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My aunt got really \Nupset back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I used to wonder \Nwhy she got so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a crush on anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's the quiet type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes heavy metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So he likes the \Nsame bands as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what made \Nyou fall for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a moment or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You called \Nyourself a working girl earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at a nearby tofu shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get enough allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even pay \Nmy cell phone bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to start \Nearning my own money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's birthday \Nis coming up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surrounded \Nby people, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've sworn \Nthis park was bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have \Ngrown up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The river of time is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd bump into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're the eldest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect? You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I only... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because \N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}my name is Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your eye because \N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}of the adoption, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a crazy assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my eye because of a sickness, \Nnot because of the adoption or any person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hold any grudges \Nto you or my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I used to think about why I had to go through all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, I thought \Nit would just be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had been put up for \Nadoption and lost your left eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then I would've suffered \Njust as much as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mei... I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that your \Nhouse over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomiyama is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I have \Nto get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to live in a city?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant because of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,School? {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to do \Nsomething with music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a music school? {you can use music school / music college / etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I went on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lighter than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll only fall with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll never let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It basically scared me dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it scared you silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be scared of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I liked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd die, but I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me half to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,'kay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw what happened at the \Namusement park and it wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so worried again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what \Nchemotherapy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leukemia can be treated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If the medicine doesn't work, I think you can \Nhave a bone marrow transplant. You can use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctors said you'd \Nbe the best donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out \Nwhen they release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday's coming up, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be your birthday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to get \Nbetter. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard nut to crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want what I saw \Nthere at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ep 1}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{ep 1}Hey, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{ep 1}Mei. Misaki Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
